WEBVTT

16:51.950 --> 16:53.210 line:80%
What Seven-Step Poem?

16:54.710 --> 16:56.040 line:80%
"Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.

16:56.040 --> 16:57.470 line:80%
The beans are sobbing inside the pot.

16:57.470 --> 16:58.680 line:80%
Both of them were born from the same root.

16:58.680 --> 17:00.160 line:80%
Why rush to torment each other?"

17:00.160 --> 17:01.290 line:80%
What does that mean?
